data.description: Welcome to a brand-new 2023 construction nestled within the tranquil and gated community of Crystal Beach by Southern Homes, conveniently situated just off US 17. This modern gem boasts 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing the perfect canvas for your family's comfort and style. Step inside, and you'll discover a home adorned with sleek and elegant tile throughout, creating an effortlessly clean and contemporary atmosphere. The expansive master bedroom is a true sanctuary, offering generous space and an attached master bathroom for added luxury and convenience. Additionally, this home features a versatile home office or flex space, providing you with the flexibility to tailor your living space to your unique needs. The open floor plan further enhances the sense of space and allows for easy flow between the different areas of the home. Crystal Beach is not just a place to call home; it's a lifestyle. Tucked away from the hustle and bustle of the city, you can savor the peace and tranquility of this gated community while still enjoying quick access to all the shopping, dining, and entertainment that Winter Haven has to offer. With Winter Haven's vibrant downtown and the excitement of Legoland Theme Park just a stone's throw away, you'll have a world of entertainment options right at your doorstep.Welcome to the future of comfortable and convenient living at Crystal Beach. **SAVE on Buyers CLOSING COST!** Call for more information and to schedule your showing today!
